 <span data-ttu-id="b28d0-105">A `FileMode` viene specificato in molti dei costruttori <xref:System.IO.FileStream>, <xref:System.IO.IsolatedStorage.IsolatedStorageFileStream>e il `Open` metodi di <xref:System.IO.File> e <xref:System.IO.FileInfo> per controllare le modalità di apertura di un file.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b28d0-105">A `FileMode` parameter is specified in many of the constructors for <xref:System.IO.FileStream>, <xref:System.IO.IsolatedStorage.IsolatedStorageFileStream>, and in the `Open` methods of <xref:System.IO.File> and <xref:System.IO.FileInfo> to control how a file is opened.</span></span>  
  
